flowchart LR
  Sources[TikTok / Meta Library / Amazon / Trends / AliExpress] --> N8N[n8n workflows]
  N8N --> API[Fastify API]
  API --> Core[Core scoring and rules]
  API --> DB[(Postgres)]
  API --> Redis[(Redis queue)]
  Redis --> Worker[Worker processors]
  Worker --> Shopify[Shopify Admin API]
  Worker --> Suppliers[Zendrop / Spocket / CJ / AutoDS / DSers]
  Shopify --> Webhooks[Shopify webhooks]
  Webhooks --> API
  Suppliers --> Tracking[Tracking callbacks]
  Tracking --> API
  API --> Admin[Next admin dashboard]
  API --> Metrics[Prometheus metrics]
  API --> Sentry[Sentry alerts]
